Name: absl_log_globals
Description: Abseil log_globals library
URL: https://abseil.io/
Version: 20230125
Requires: absl_atomic_hook = 20230125, absl_config = 20230125, absl_core_headers = 20230125, absl_hash = 20230125, absl_log_severity = 20230125, absl_strings = 20230125
